.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, mystery, superhero, epic
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: dubstep, classical, reggae, disco
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: volleyball, ice-hockey, lacrosse, handball
1. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
2. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the person watching superhero movies##3
5. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is volleyball##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is the fan of dubstep##1
7. the fan of reggae is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family  | epic   | superhero     | mystery |
| Music-Genre   | reggae  | disco      | dubstep        | classical     |
| Sport         | lacrosse | volleyball | handball | ice-hockey   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, nigerian, british, egyptian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, handball, parkour, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, bike, subway, ship
1. the egyptian is the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the british is in an odd position##4
3. the person driving the motorbike is the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
5. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
6. the person who's sport is handball is on the far left##1
7. the nigerian is on the far right##1
8. the british is on the left or right of the person driving the subway##3
9. the person who's sport is cycling is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | malaysian   | egyptian   | british | nigerian |
| Sport         | handball      | basketball | cycling      | parkour |
| Transport     | bike | motorbike        | ship       | subway  |

