.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
There 4 different types of food: nectarine, corn, kale, radish
The people have 4 different hobbies: traveling, video-games, chess, gardening
4 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, pony, snake
1. the person eating corn is in an odd position##4
2. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the owner of the ferret is the person eating corn##1
4. the person eating kale is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far right##1
6. the person eating radish is on the left of the person eating corn##1
7. the person eating radish is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | kale   | radish      | corn       | nectarine |
| Hobby   | traveling | gardening | chess     | video-games |
| Pet     | snake     | hedgehog  | ferret | pony |

