.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, juice, water, coffee
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, spy, documentary, drama
4 different pets are kept: ferret, rabbit, cat, turtle
1. the owner of the cat is the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is between the person watching drama movies and the owner of the ferret##2
3. the person watching drama movies is the person drinking juice##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is in an even position##4
6. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage      | water   | coffee          | juice | soy-milk        |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | spy | drama   | adventure     |
| Pet           | ferret | rabbit         | turtle         | cat |

