.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, gardening, card-games, baking
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, chef, entrepreneur, videographer
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, d&b, soul, gospel
1. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the fan of soul##3
2. the entrepreneur is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the videographer is the person who's hobby is card-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the fan of soul##1
5. the fan of d&b is between the fisherman and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
6. the fan of gospel is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
7. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's hobby is card-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Hobby         | gardening | rock-climbing      | card-games       | baking    |
| Job           | chef  | entrepreneur  | videographer | fisherman |
| Music-Genre   | gospel      | soul | d&b         | rock    |

