.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, sprite, lemonade
The people have 4 different jobs:  teacher, software-developer, dancer, freelancer
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: swimming, biathlon, skateboarding, lemonade-polo
1. the teacher is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the teacher##3
3. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the teacher##3
4. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3
6. the person who's sport is lemonade-polo is on the right of the teacher##1
7. the teacher is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
8. the software-developer is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
9. the freelancer is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage   | almond-milk         | soy-milk  | sprite     | lemonade         |
| Job        | freelancer | software-developer | teacher | dancer         |
| Sport      | biathlon         | skateboarding  | swimming   | lemonade-polo |

