.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, trance, gospel, ambient
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, egyptian, pakistani, french
4 different pets are kept: frog, bird, hamster, rat
 1. the owner of the hamster is on the left or right of the fan of gospel##3
 2. the mexican is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 4. the pakistani is between the fan of trance and the fan of classical##2
 5. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the fan of trance##3
 6. the owner of the rat is the fan of gospel##1
 7. the french is on the far right##1
 8. the fan of classical is in an odd position##4
 9. the egyptian is between the fan of ambient and the fan of gospel##2
10. the owner of the hamster is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | gospel    | trance | ambient    |
| Nationality   | mexican | pakistani | egyptian  | french |
| Pet           | hamster   | rat    | frog        | bird   |

