.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, sprite, tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, musician, entrepreneur, lawyer
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, colombian, canadian, thai
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left or far right##3
2. the musician is on the left of the bartender##1
3. the thai is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
4. the musician is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the bartender##1
6. the thai is on the right of the musician##1
7. the colombian is on the left of the musician##1
8. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the colombian##3
9. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the pakistani##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage      | iced-tea                | tea  | milk | sprite   |
| Job           | lawyer | musician | bartender   | entrepreneur |
| Nationality   | colombian         | pakistani     | thai     | canadian |

