.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pear, potato, garlic, pomegranate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, zombie, family, scientific
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, trance, electronic, disco
1. the person eating potato is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person eating garlic is on the far left##1
3. the fan of trance is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
4. the person eating garlic is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
5. the fan of metal is between the person watching scientific movies and the fan of disco##2
6. the person watching family movies is in an even position##4
7. the person eating pear is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | garlic    | potato  | pomegranate  | pear |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | zombie | thriller | family |
| Music-Genre   | electronic    | metal     | disco    | trance |

