.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, hot-chocolate, water
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, french, dutch, japanese
4 different pets are kept: mouse, frog, hedgehog, goldfish
1. the owner of the frog is between the person drinking hot-chocolate and the italian##2
2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
3. the dutch is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the french##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the owner of the hedgehog##3
7. the italian is on the left or right of the japanese##3
8. the dutch is the person drinking 7up##1
9. the japanese is between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the mouse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Beverage      | 7up | hot-chocolate      | cola  | water    |
| Nationality   | dutch   | french | japanese | italian |
| Pet           | goldfish      | hedgehog       | frog   | mouse      |

