.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, singing, reading, card-games
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, american, spanish, italian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's sport is skiing##2
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is card-games is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the italian is between the person who's sport is skiing and the mexican##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far right##1
8. the american is in an even position##4
9. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | photography    | reading | singing  | card-games  |
| Nationality   | spanish | american       | italian | mexican |
| Sport         | sailing   | skiing      | weightlifting | ice-hockey       |

