4. the person drinking coffee is the person watching adventure movies##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is the owner of the rabbit##1
7. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the person drinking water##1
8. the owner of the chinchilla is the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
