.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, coffee, 7up
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, volleyball, rugby, lacrosse
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, quad-bike, train, van
1. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
5. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is rugby##2
6. the person driving the subway is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
7. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1
8. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | coffee    | almond-milk     | water    | 7up        |
| Sport       | rugby   | biathlon | volleyball | lacrosse |
| Transport   | van | train      | quad-bike    | subway   |

