4. the person eating papaya is on the far left or far right##3
5. the american is on the left of the indian##1
6. the person eating papaya is in an odd position##4
7. the british is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person eating banana is the person watching musical movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
