4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the chef##1
5. the indonesian is on the right of the japanese##1
6. the accountant is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the firefighter##1
8. the argentine is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |        4        |
| Hobby         | chess | woodworking   | hiking    | filmmaking    |
| Job           | musician   | chef    | accountant | firefighter |
| Nationality   | argentine    | japanese | indonesian    | american         |

