3. the fan of pop is on the far left##1
4. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of techno##1
5. the person watching comedy movies is the german##1
6. the fan of soul is on the right of the american##1
7. the american is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
8. the fan of pop is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | family | scientific | comedy | musical   |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | techno   | soul     | dubstep    |
| Nationality   | mexican  | american | german  | spanish |

