.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
There 4 different types of food: cranberry, cherry, lettuce, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, puzzles, gardening, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, dog, fish
1. the person eating cranberry is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the lizard is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3
4. the person eating lettuce is on the far left##1
5. the person eating cherry is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person who's hobby is photography##2
6. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
7. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
8. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person eating cherry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food    | lettuce    | cherry    | cranberry  | tomato |
| Hobby   | woodworking | puzzles | photography | gardening      |
| Pet     | goldfish   | lizard        | fish   | dog       |

 